a===\n* [[Hugh Culling Eardley Childers]], 1857\u20131858\n* [[Charles Pasley (engineer)|Charles Pasley]], 1864\u20131867 (acting)\n* [[George Frederic Verdon]], 1867\u20131872\n* [[Hugh Culling Eardley Childers]], 1872\u20131873\n* [[James McCulloch]], 1873 (acting from January to April)\n* [[Archibald Michie]], 1873\u20131879\n* [[Charles Pasley (engineer)|Charles Pasley]], 1880\u20131882 (acting)\n* [[Robert Murray Smith]], 1882\u20131886\n* [[Graham Berry]], 1886\u20131891\n* [[James Munro (Australian politician)|James Munro]], 1892\u20131893\n* [[Duncan Gillies]], 1893\u20131897\n* [[Andrew Clarke (administrator)|Andrew Clarke]], 1897\u20131902 (and for Tasmania)\n* [[John William Taverner]], 1903\u20131913\n* [[Peter McBride (politician)|Peter McBride]],<ref>{{cite book |first=Andrew |last=Spaull |chapter=McBride, Sir Peter (1867\u20131923) |title=Australian Dictionary of Biography |volume=10 |pages=205\u2013206 |publisher=National Centre of Biography, Australian National University |chapterurl=http://adb.anu.edu.au/biography/mcbride-sir-peter-7295/text12653 |year=1986 |accessdate=27 September 2016}}</ref><ref>{{London Gazette |issue=32095 |date=22 October 1920 |page=10197}}</ref> 1913\u20131922\n* [[John McWhae]], 1922\u20131924\n* [[George Fairbairn (politician)|George Fairbairn]], 1924\u20131927\n* [[Walter Leitch]], 1929\u20131933\n* [[Richard Linton (politician)|Richard Linton]], 1933\u20131936\n* [[Murray William James Bourchier]], 1936\u20131937\n* [[Albert Louis Bussau]], 1938\u20131944\n* [[Norman Angus Martin]], 1945\u20131950\n* [[John Lienhop|John Henry Lienhop]], 1950\u20131956\n* [[William Watt Leggatt]], 1956\u2013 1964\n* [[Sir Horace Petty]], 1964\u20131969\n* [[John Rossiter|Sir John Rossiter]] 1976&ndash;1979\n* The Hon. Joseph Anstice Rafferty 1979-1983\n* [[Ian Haig]], 1983\u20131985\n* Kenneth Andrew Finnin, 1985\u20131988\n* [[Ian Haig]], 1988\u20131989\n* [[Alan Brown (Australian politician)|Alan Brown]], 1996\u20132000\n* Peter Hansen,